annotations.title: 5 EASY GIN COCKTAIL RECIPES!

textContent:
1.5 oz gin
0.75 oz St-Germain
0.75 oz Lime juice
1.5 oz Soda water or sparkling water

Shake and strain over ice into highball
Top with club soda
